        "y": 27
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi ng\u00e0nh \u2014 CDC Pipeline\n\n| Metric | **Pipeline n\u00e0y** | Debezium docs | Databricks RTM (2026) | Netflix (2025) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| **E2E latency p50** | **2.02s** | ~ms (DB\u2192Kafka only, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh Spark) | <200ms (7\u00d7 i3.2xlarge cloud) | seconds (analytics CDC) |\n| **E2E latency p99** | **4.05s** | N/A | <500ms | N/A |\n| **Throughput E2E** | **35 ev/s** | ~7,000 ev/s (connector max, single-threaded) | 100K+ ev/s | 100M ev/s (Data Mesh) |\n| **Redis p99 read** | **<1ms** | N/A | N/A | <100\u03bcs (near-cache) |\n| **Sync rate** | **100%** | at-least-once | exactly-once | exactly-once |\n| **Infra** | **1 laptop \u00b7 Docker** | 2\u00d7 EC2 c5a.xlarge | 7\u00d7 i3.2xlarge | K8s \u00b7 multi-DC \u00b7 10K+ engineers |\n\n### Key Insights\n- **Bottleneck = Spark trigger 2s**, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Kafka (experiment: partition 1\u21923 ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng +0.4%)\n- **Trigger 2s** \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng experiment: batch processing ~1200ms \u2192 min safe trigger = 1200 \u00d7 1.5 = 1800ms \u2192 2s\n- **Redis <1ms** \u0111\u1ea1t industry standard \u2014 serving layer kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bottleneck\n- **Debezium ch\u1ec9 \u0111o DB\u2192Kafka (~ms)** \u2014 pipeline n\u00e0y \u0111o full E2E bao g\u1ed3m Spark batch window\n- Mu\u1ed1n <200ms c\u1ea7n Spark 4.x RTM ho\u1eb7c Flink + cloud cluster"
      }
    }
